01:59:38.990 --> 01:59:40.620
我以为你不会开口
Thought you'd never ask.

939
01:59:41.210 --> 01:59:43.330
马上赶去  启动遥控模式
Crawler's on the way. Initiating remote mode.

940
02:00:13.490 --> 02:00:14.490
谢了  阿尔弗雷德
Thank you, Alfred.

941
02:00:14.660 --> 02:00:16.070
不客气
Don't mention it.

942
02:00:38.800 --> 02:00:39.760
惨了
No!

943
02:00:47.770 --> 02:00:49.230
他们安全了  回去隧道
They're safe. Get back to the tunnel.

944
02:00:49.400 --> 02:00:52.480
隧道  好  外星人  坏蛋  耍剑的女士
Tunnel. Right. Aliens, bad guy, sword lady.

945
02:01:04.290 --> 02:01:05.660
轮到我
My turn.

946
02:02:28.040 --> 02:02:29.540
系统全面故障
Catastrophic failure of all systems.

947
02:02:29.710 --> 02:02:32.130
你没事吧  韦恩少爷
Are you all right, Master Wayne?

948
02:02:32.290 --> 02:02:33.290
你没事吧
Are you all right?

949
02:02:44.010 --> 02:02:47.520
你身上流着旧神族的血液
You have the blood of the old gods in you.

950
02:03:01.990 --> 02:03:02.820
你没事吧
You okay?

951
02:03:04.830 --> 02:03:06.450
我不确定你会来
Wasn't sure you'd come.

952
02:03:07.490 --> 02:03:08.790
你是我父亲
You're my father.

953
02:03:12.290 --> 02:03:13.290
快去吧
Go.

954
02:03:26.930 --> 02:03:27.930
不要
No!

955
02:04:13.440 --> 02:04:15.770
放轻松  阿尔弗雷德  我来接手
Relax, Alfred. I'll take it from here.

956
02:04:17.980 --> 02:04:19.190
我认识你吗
Uh, do I know you?

957
02:04:50.100 --> 02:04:51.350
我们在哪里的下面
What are we under, right now?

958
02:04:52.100 --> 02:04:53.390
哥谭港
Gotham Harbor.

959
02:05:32.100 --> 02:05:33.390
那是谁
Who is that?

960
02:05:58.710 --> 02:05:59.880
快点
Come on.

961
02:06:05.010 --> 02:06:06.220
戴安娜  快上来
Diana, get on!

962
02:07:08.110 --> 02:07:09.610
是什么
What is it?

963
02:07:17.410 --> 02:07:18.830
让我看
Show me.

964
02:07:57.990 --> 02:07:59.620
它在这里
It is here.

965
02:08:00.370 --> 02:08:03.330
在这个世界
On this world.

966
02:08:37.240 --> 02:08:40.200
你可能感染了外星微生物  必须接受隔离
Sir, you're gonna be in quarantine for possible alien microbes.

967
02:08:40.370 --> 02:08:42.040
美国政府的规定要求…
U.S. government protocols require that...

968
02:08:42.200 --> 02:08:45.000
我知道规定  是我写的
I know the requirements. I wrote them.

969
02:08:49.550 --> 02:08:50.880
它召唤了他
It called to him.

970
02:08:51.050 --> 02:08:52.590
母盒
The Mother Box.

971
02:08:52.760 --> 02:08:54.130
他抢走的那个
The one he already has.

972
02:08:54.470 --> 02:08:57.510
他有两个了  他从亚特兰蒂斯抢走母盒
He has two. He took the Mother Box from Atlantis.

973
02:08:57.680 --> 02:08:59.970
现在只需要人类遗失的母盒
All he needs now is the lost Box of Men.

974
02:09:00.140 --> 02:09:01.310
他可能已经拿到手了
If he doesn't already have it.

975
02:09:04.980 --> 02:09:06.400
他没有拿到手
He doesn't have it.

976
02:09:09.610 --> 02:09:10.770
在我这里
I do.

977
02:09:21.330 --> 02:09:23.410
你完成征服行动了吗
Have you finished the conquest?

978
02:09:23.580 --> 02:09:24.830
还没有  狄萨德
Not yet, DeSaad.

979
02:09:25.000 --> 02:09:27.250
那你为何召唤我
Then why do you summon me?

980
02:09:27.420 --> 02:09:29.080
我带来消息
I bring news.

981
02:09:29.250 --> 02:09:32.170
强大的达克赛德登上王位之前
Before mighty Darkseid came to the throne,

982
02:09:32.340 --> 02:09:36.840
他在全宇宙搜寻终极武器
he searched the universe for the ultimate weapon.

983
02:09:37.470 --> 02:09:39.640
反生命方程序
The Anti-Life Equation.

984
02:09:39.800 --> 02:09:44.480
掌控多重宇宙中  所有生命与自由意志的关键
The key to controlling all life and all will throughout the multiverse.

985
02:09:44.640 --> 02:09:47.650
他发现它被藏在一个原始星球上  但在他还没…
He found it hidden on a primitive planet, but before...

986
02:09:47.810 --> 02:09:50.690
大家都知道你背叛了他
The story of the defiance is well-known.

987
02:09:50.860 --> 02:09:53.360
我找到了那个原始星球
I have found the primitive planet.

988
02:09:53.530 --> 02:09:55.570
胆敢反击的世界
The world that fought back.

989
02:09:55.740 --> 02:09:57.610
就是地球
It is Earth.

990
02:09:57.780 --> 02:09:59.990
反生命方程序被刻在…
The Anti-Life Equation is carved

991
02:10:00.160 --> 02:10:04.040
这个世界的地表
into the surface of this very world.

992
02:10:07.710 --> 02:10:09.120
你确定
Are you certain?

993
02:10:09.290 --> 02:10:10.330
我看到了
I have seen it.

994
02:10:10.500 --> 02:10:13.920
我亲眼看到了
I have looked with my own eyes.

995
02:10:57.260 --> 02:10:58.840
主人
My lord.

996
02:11:00.380 --> 02:11:03.930
荒原狼
Oh, Steppenwolf.

997
02:11:04.600 --> 02:11:07.680
主人  我只是你谦卑的仆人
My lord, I am but your humble servant.

998
02:11:08.680 --> 02:11:11.520
你真的找到它了
Can it be true that you have found it?

999
02:11:11.690 --> 02:11:13.860
是的  霸主
I have, great one.

1000
02:11:14.610 --> 02:11:17.570
失落的世界就是地球
The lost world is Earth.

1001
02:11:17.740 --> 02:11:20.740
反生命方程序就在这里
Anti-Life is here.

1002
02:11:22.070 --> 02:11:25.410
你若想寻求救赎  那就找到第三个母盒
If it is redemption you seek, find the third box,

1003
02:11:25.580 --> 02:11:28.540
合而为一形成三位一体  当这世界化为焦土
synchronize The Unity, and when this world is scorched,

1004
02:11:28.700 --> 02:11:31.920
我就会来拿我的大奖
I will come for my great prize.

1005
02:11:32.880 --> 02:11:35.090
你会来地球
You will come to Earth?

1006
02:11:36.130 --> 02:11:40.380
我已经把十万个世界化为尘土
I have turned 100,000 worlds to dust

1007
02:11:40.550 --> 02:11:42.050
寻找反生命方程序
looking for Anti-Life.

1008
02:11:42.220 --> 02:11:45.430
寻找抢走我荣耀之人
Looking for those who robbed me of my glory.

1009
02:11:45.600 --> 02:11:51.350
我将踏着他们的骨骸  沐浴在反生命方程序的荣光中
I will stride across their bones and bask in the glow of Anti-Life.

1010
02:11:51.520 --> 02:11:54.230
所有的生命
And all of existence

1011
02:11:54.400 --> 02:11:57.900
都将是我的
shall be mine.

1012
02:12:01.280 --> 02:12:05.200
一定会的  主人
It shall be so, my master.

1013
02:12:09.410 --> 02:12:11.080
酷爆了
So cool.

1014
02:12:11.250 --> 02:12:13.790
从外面看  这只是一栋废弃建筑物
From the outside, it looks like this building was abandoned.

1015
02:12:17.540 --> 02:12:19.300
它想要飞行
It wants to fly.

1016
02:12:20.510 --> 02:12:22.380
你和机器说话
You talk to machines?

1017
02:12:22.680 --> 02:12:24.680
我和人工智能说话
I speak to intelligence.

1018
02:12:24.840 --> 02:12:27.720
这个说她因为软体问题不能飞
This one's saying she can't fly because of a software issue,

1019
02:12:27.890 --> 02:12:29.850
不过我很快就能修好
but I could fix it with a little time.

1020
02:12:39.610 --> 02:12:41.820
我的数据流中有个黑点
There's a dark spot in my data stream.

1021
02:12:42.150 --> 02:12:44.410
我能感应到另外两个母盒
I could feel the other two boxes.

1022
02:12:44.570 --> 02:12:46.410
我知道它们苏醒了
I know they're awake,

1023
02:12:46.570 --> 02:12:48.080
但是看不见它们在哪里
but I can't see where they are.

1024
02:12:48.240 --> 02:12:50.240
知道敌方基地在哪里才能攻击
Well, we can't attack unless we know where the base is.

1025
02:12:50.410 --> 02:12:52.660
就算我们知道
Even if we knew,

1026
02:12:52.830 --> 02:12:55.670
也没有比荒原狼更强大的生物
I've never seen a being as strong as Steppenwolf.

1027
02:12:57.880 --> 02:12:59.250
也许有一个
Maybe one.

1028
02:12:59.630 --> 02:13:01.010
超人
Hmm, Superman.

1029
02:13:01.920 --> 02:13:05.970
只要第三个母盒在沉睡  他们就看不到它  只能感应到它
As long as the third box is asleep, they can't see it, only sense it.

1030
02:13:06.140 --> 02:13:08.180
我们得不断移动才不会被发现
We need to keep moving so they can't catch up.

1031
02:13:08.350 --> 02:13:11.520
不  这只是延缓失败的策略  不是获胜的战略
No. That's just a strategy to lose more slowly, not to win.

1032
02:13:12.140 --> 02:13:14.140
难道火焰喷射器不流行了吗
Remind me, are flamethrowers not a thing?

1033
02:13:15.020 --> 02:13:16.100
为何不直接烧毁它
Why don't we just destroy it?

1034
02:13:16.270 --> 02:13:18.360
烈火也无法摧毁母盒
Fire doesn't destroy the boxes.

1035
02:13:18.520 --> 02:13:20.270
它们是一种未知的物质
They're an unknown form of matter.

1036
02:13:20.440 --> 02:13:23.900
喜欢热能  会吸收它  保存在它们的核心
Oh, they love heat. They absorb it, hold it in their cores.

1037
02:13:24.070 --> 02:13:26.200
你很了解这些盒子嘛
Well, you know a lot about these boxes.

1038
02:13:26.780 --> 02:13:28.030
非常可疑
Makes you think.

1039
02:13:28.200 --> 02:13:29.910
你在哪里找到母盒
Where'd you find the box, Victor?

1040
02:13:30.870 --> 02:13:32.290
你在怀疑我吗
Are you trying to say something?

1041
02:13:32.580 --> 02:13:34.080
我就是怀疑你
Oh, I'm saying it.

1042
02:13:34.660 --> 02:13:36.540
我们怎么知道你不是他们的奸细
How do we know you're not working for them?

1043
02:13:38.420 --> 02:13:40.090
说来话长
It's a long story.

1044
02:13:40.540 --> 02:13:42.460
你赶着要去哪儿吗
You got somewhere else to be?

1045
02:13:49.850 --> 02:13:53.680
纳粹在二战结束前找到母盒
The Nazis found the box at the end of the Second World War,

1046
02:13:53.850 --> 02:13:56.890
它被埋在一座义大利修道院底下
buried under an Italian monastery.

1047
02:13:57.060 --> 02:13:59.440
被送去给希特勒的路上  遭到盟军拦截
The Allies intercepted it on its way to Hitler.

1048
02:13:59.610 --> 02:14:01.820
1944年被带回了美国
They brought it back to the States in '44.

1049
02:14:02.400 --> 02:14:05.950
6-1-9-8-2号未知物件
Unknown object 6-1-9-8-2.

1050
02:14:06.820 --> 02:14:10.280
它被丢在五角大厦档案室七十年
It collected dust in the Pentagon archives for 70 years

1051
02:14:10.820 --> 02:14:14.040
直到国防部开始研究超人飞船
till DoD began to study the Superman ship.

1052
02:14:15.580 --> 02:14:19.080
星辰实验室的一位研究员  发现超人飞船和…
A researcher at STARLABS made a connection between the ship...

1053
02:14:20.380 --> 02:14:21.920
6-1-9-8-2号物件有关联
and 6-1-9-8-2.

1054
02:14:22.800 --> 02:14:25.630
他了解到它们都是外星科技
He understood they were both alien technologies.

1055
02:14:26.300 --> 02:14:27.880
不同的文明
Different civilizations,

1056
02:14:28.470 --> 02:14:30.590
类似的属性
similar properties.

1057
02:14:31.930 --> 02:14:34.680
虽然母盒已经沉睡了几千年
And though the box had slept for thousands of years,

1058
02:14:35.350 --> 02:14:38.190
那位研究员想出  一个可以唤醒它的理论
the researcher formulated a theory on how to awaken it.

1059
02:14:38.810 --> 02:14:40.560
也真的唤醒了它
And so did.

1060
02:14:43.020 --> 02:14:43.860
后来…
Then...

1061
02:14:45.990 --> 02:14:47.900
我出了车祸  本来应该死去
I had an accident that should've killed me.

1062
02:14:49.240 --> 02:14:52.450
但是出于绝望或是疯狂
But in an act of desperation or madness,

1063
02:14:52.620 --> 02:14:54.950
那位研究员驾驭了母盒的力量
the researcher harnessed the power of the Mother Box.

1064
02:15:11.140 --> 02:15:13.220
释放了一种他无法…
He unleashed an alien technology

1065
02:15:13.390 --> 02:15:16.060
完全理解的外星科技
he didn't fully understand.

1066
02:15:16.220 --> 02:15:18.600
他利用那股力量让我活下来
He used that power to keep me alive.

1067
02:15:22.190 --> 02:15:23.770
活着…
Alive...

1068
02:15:24.320 --> 02:15:26.280
但变成了这样
but turned into this.

1069
02:15:29.070 --> 02:15:31.360
母盒继续沉睡
The box went back to sleep

1070
02:15:32.280 --> 02:15:33.950
他也没有物归原处
and he never returned it.

1071
02:15:36.580 --> 02:15:38.620
那位研究员就是塞拉斯·斯通
That researcher was Silas Stone.

1072
02:15:40.330 --> 02:15:42.000
我的父亲
My father.

1073
02:15:45.290 --> 02:15:46.960
等等
Wait,

1074
02:15:47.130 --> 02:15:50.510
你父亲用一个母盒救了你一命
your father saved your life with one of these things?

1075
02:15:50.670 --> 02:15:52.890
它们不是变态杀人机器吗
Aren't they psycho murder machines?

1076
02:15:53.050 --> 02:15:55.430
它们是改造机器
They're change machines.

1077
02:15:55.600 --> 02:15:58.270
母盒没有救人或杀人…
The boxes don't think in terms of healing or killing,

1078
02:15:58.680 --> 02:16:00.770
活着或死亡的概念
alive or dead.

1079
02:16:00.930 --> 02:16:03.190
它们按照主人的意愿重新排列物质
They rearrange matter at the will of their masters,

1080
02:16:03.350 --> 02:16:04.940
使其再生  恢复原状
regenerate, reinstate.

1081
02:16:05.110 --> 02:16:06.520
恢复原状
Reinstate?

1082
02:16:06.690 --> 02:16:10.110
母盒拥有恢复粒子相互作用的力量
A box has the power to reinstate anterior particle relationships.

1083
02:16:10.280 --> 02:16:13.360
你是说任何物质的粒子  都不能被创造或毁灭
So, you mean in the way that particles of matter can't be created or destroyed,

1084
02:16:13.530 --> 02:16:15.530
它们的相互作用只会转变
their relations just transform.

1085
02:16:15.700 --> 02:16:18.450
烧掉一栋房子  粒子仍然存在
Burn down a house, the particles still exist.

1086
02:16:18.620 --> 02:16:21.080
房子的粒子变成灰烬的粒子
Particles of house become particles of smoke.

1087
02:16:21.250 --> 02:16:25.290
任何人只要有火柴  都能把一栋房子化成灰烬
Anybody with a match can turn a house to smoke.

1088
02:16:27.340 --> 02:16:29.090
但是一个母盒
But a Mother Box...

1089
02:16:29.250 --> 02:16:31.470
能够把灰烬变回一栋房子
...turns smoke back into a house.

1090
02:16:37.470 --> 02:16:39.970
我知道我们都在想同样的事
I know we're all thinking the same thing right now.

1091
02:16:41.430 --> 02:16:43.940
谁要说我才不说
Who's gonna say it? I'm not gonna say it.

1092
02:17:11.210 --> 02:17:12.300
谁啊
Who is it?

1093
02:17:13.010 --> 02:17:14.220
玛莎
Martha.

1094
02:17:32.570 --> 02:17:37.570
我去了星球日报  终于拿回克拉克的东西
I went to the Daily Planet to finally pick up Clark's things.

1095
02:17:39.070 --> 02:17:42.370
不知道为什么  现在无处可放
I don't know why, nowhere to put them now.

1096
02:17:45.160 --> 02:17:46.790
我失去了农场
I lost the farm.

1097
02:17:48.420 --> 02:17:50.540
我迟缴房贷好一阵子了
I'd been behind on the payments for a while.

1098
02:17:51.920 --> 02:17:55.800
老实说  那房子我一个人住太大了
Truth is, the house is too big for me to live in by myself anyway.

1099
02:17:56.340 --> 02:17:59.140
你知道我随时都欢迎你来住
Well, you know you're welcome to stay here any time

1100
02:17:59.300 --> 02:18:01.260
只要你需要的话
for as long as you need.

1101
02:18:02.470 --> 02:18:05.100
谢谢你  露易丝  你真好心
Thank you, Lois. That's very kind.

1102
02:18:06.770 --> 02:18:08.850
但我找到一个小地方  我一个人住刚好
But I've found a little place that suits me just fine,

1103
02:18:09.020 --> 02:18:10.480
就在餐馆旁边
right by the diner.

1104
02:18:11.110 --> 02:18:12.480
我不是来求助的
I'm not here for help.

1105
02:18:13.650 --> 02:18:15.530
我来是因为…
I'm here because

1106
02:18:16.360 --> 02:18:18.780
我见到派瑞先生  他跟我说…
when I saw Mr. Perry, he told me that

1107
02:18:20.240 --> 02:18:23.160
克拉克死后你就没去上班了
you haven't been to work since Clark died.

1108
02:18:27.960 --> 02:18:29.580
我办不到
I can't.

1109
02:18:36.470 --> 02:18:38.800
全世界都在哀悼
The whole world is mourning.

1110
02:18:40.430 --> 02:18:42.850
为了一个象征悲伤
Grieving over a symbol.

1111
02:18:43.010 --> 02:18:46.810
我走到哪儿都看到那个"S"
Everywhere I go, everywhere I look, I see that "S."

1112
02:18:47.940 --> 02:18:49.940
也听到人们在说什么
I hear what people say.

1113
02:18:50.100 --> 02:18:51.940
好像他们都认识他
They talk like they knew him.

1114
02:18:53.150 --> 02:18:55.400
但是他们不认识克拉克
But they didn't know Clark.

1115
02:18:56.940 --> 02:18:59.280
我不能拦住他们
And I can't stop them

1116
02:18:59.450 --> 02:19:00.820
看着他们跟他们说
and look at them

1117
02:19:00.990 --> 02:19:03.740
我为我儿子感到多么骄傲
and tell them how proud I am of my son.

1118
02:19:05.740 --> 02:19:08.250
只有你知道
