And we have to assume he's won.

1509
02:58:41.500 --> 02:58:44.620
我才不管他在多少个地狱  打过多少恶魔
I don't care how many demons he's fought in how many hells...

1510
02:58:44.790 --> 02:58:48.290
他没打过我们  团结一致的我们
he's never fought us. Not us united.

1511
02:59:38.760 --> 02:59:40.390
我猜你说"愿意"
Take that as a "yes."

1512
02:59:41.010 --> 02:59:41.850
什么
What?

1513
