I have a second chance, Lo.

1516
03:00:29.810 --> 03:00:32.270
绝对不会白白浪费
And I am not gonna waste it.

1517
03:01:30.540 --> 03:01:31.710
真的是你吗
Are you really you?

1518
03:01:31.870 --> 03:01:33.580
真的是我  妈
I'm really me, Ma.

1519
03:01:51.600 --> 03:01:53.650
听好  妈
Listen, Ma.

1520
03:01:55.230 --> 03:01:57.270
