I never said that.

1529
03:02:59.550 --> 03:03:00.960
怎么了
What is it?

1530
03:03:04.880 --> 03:03:09.890
我做过一个梦  不晓得  几乎就像一种预感
I had a dream, like, I don't know, almost like a premonition.

1531
03:03:10.850 --> 03:03:13.640
