1532
03:03:13.810 --> 03:03:16.650
巴里·艾伦就在这里
and Barry Allen was right here

1533
03:03:16.810 --> 03:03:20.690
他跟我说  "露易丝·莱恩才是关键"
and he said to me, "Lois Lane is the key."

1534
03:03:23.360 --> 03:03:26.570
对超人来说…她是
She is... to Superman.

1535
03:03:27.620 --> 03:03:29.240
每个人都有心爱的人
Every heart has one.

1536
03:03:29.870 --> 03:03:31.740
我想不只是这样
I think it's something more.

1537
03:03:32.620 --> 03:03:34.500
这是更黑暗的东西
Something darker.

1538
03:03:38.670 --> 03:03:39.670
韦恩少爷
Master Wayne.

1539
03:03:39.840 --> 03:03:41.340
韦恩少爷
Master Wayne!

1540
03:03:42.170 --> 03:03:43.840
你得来看看
You need to see this.

1541
