They will join you in the sun, Kal.

1589
03:07:46.580 --> 03:07:50.540
你必须选择是否要  骄傲地站在全人类面前
A choice of whether to stand proud in front of the human race or not.

1590
03:07:50.710 --> 03:07:53.880
你将帮助他们完成奇迹
You will help them accomplish wonders.

1591
03:08:11.020 --> 03:08:15.530
氪星所有的希望和梦想  都寄托在你身上
All the hopes and dreams of Krypton live in you now.

1592
03:08:15.690 --> 03:08:17.950
我真为你感到骄傲  儿子
I'm so proud of you, son.

1593
03:08:19.280 --> 03:08:21.330
你母亲和我都很爱你
Your mother and I loved you.

1594
03:08:21.990 --> 03:08:25.540
你母亲和我都知道你会改变世界
Your mother and I knew you would change the world.

1595
03:08:26.830 --> 03:08:28.670
你的心受到考验
Your heart was tested.

1596
03:08:29.960 --> 03:08:31.920
我知道这很难  克拉克
I know it's been hard, Clark.

1597
03:08:32.670 --> 03:08:35.590
但你给了他们的世界一个希望
But you gave hope to their world.

1598
03:08:35.760 --> 03:08:38.430
