1603
03:09:53.210 --> 03:09:56.340
我要把塔台射倒  破坏力场圆顶
I'm gonna take out that tower and knock down that shield dome.

1604
03:09:56.500 --> 03:09:57.630
不管你们看到什么
Whatever you see,

1605
