03:50:22.010 --> 03:50:24.930
还是觉得带着他是个好主意吗
Still think it was a good idea bringing him along?

1873
03:50:26.020 --> 03:50:27.560
你觉得呢
-what do you think?

1874
03:50:33.650 --> 03:50:34.650
他找到我们了
He's found us.

1875
03:52:03.820 --> 03:52:05.280
我能帮你吗
Can I help you?

1876
03:52:06.660 --> 03:52:10.160
你一定知道达克赛德不会放过地球
I'm sure you know Darkseid is not finished with Earth.

1877
03:52:10.330 --> 03:52:13.330
反生命方程序就在这里
The Anti-Life Equation is here somewhere.

1878
03:52:13.500 --> 03:52:16.290
我们得赶在他之前找到它
We have to find it before he does.

1879
03:52:16.460 --> 03:52:18.170
决战时刻即将到来
There's a war coming.

1880
03:52:18.460 --> 03:52:20.210
我是来帮忙的
And I'm here to help.

1881
03:52:20.380 --> 03:52:22.630
抱歉  你是哪位
I'm sorry, who are you again?

1882
03:52:22.800 --> 03:52:27.890
我有很多名字和很多形体  就像你一样…
I've gone by many names and taken many forms. And like you,

1883
03:52:28.510 --> 03:52:31.140
我发现自己要对这世界负责
I've realized I have a stake in this world

1884
03:52:31.310 --> 03:52:33.770
我也该为它而战了
and it's time I started fighting for it.

1885
03:52:37.310 --> 03:52:39.440
我们是需要帮助
Well, we could definitely use the help.

1886
03:52:39.650 --> 03:52:42.860
所以很高兴你来了
So, glad you're here.

1887
03:52:44.110 --> 03:52:46.280
我没想过会看到地球的守护者
You know, I never thought I'd see the defenders of Earth

1888
03:52:46.450 --> 03:52:48.620
会团结一致  并肩作战
united and fighting as one.

1889
03:52:49.620 --> 03:52:52.000
没有你就不会发生  布鲁斯
It wouldn't have happened without you, Bruce.

1890
03:52:53.460 --> 03:52:55.830
你父母会为你感到骄傲
Your mother and father would be proud.

1891
03:52:57.210 --> 03:52:58.380
希望如此
I hope so.

1892
03:53:04.430 --> 03:53:07.390
我会保持联系
Well, I'll be in touch.

1893
03:53:08.430 --> 03:53:12.470
对了  有些人叫我…
Oh, and some have called me

1894
03:53:12.640 --> 03:53:14.940
火星猎人
the Martian Manhunter.

1895
03:53:22.650 --> 03:53:24.990
我猜我会再见到你
I guess I'll see you around.

1896
03:53:55.430 --> 03:54:01.530
献给奥特姆

